                <note rend="inline" type="source">611.6731/119: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in Turkey</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Grew</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Paraphrase]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1929-03-27T15:00:00-05:00"
                            >March 27, 1929—3 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>17. You are authorized, in accordance with the procedure you outlined in your 17,
                    March 24, 11 a.m., paragraph numbered 2, to proceed with a new exchange of
                    notes.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Kellogg</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
